    </div>

    <div class="b-logo-text">
      <h1 class="b-logo">ColorSnapper</h1>
      <h2 class="b-tagline">The missing color picker for Mac</h2>
      <p>ColorSnapper is an easy-to-use tool for quickly finding out the color of any pixel on the screen. It is activated via a system-wide hotkey, giving you a magnifying loupe to easily pick the pixel you need. The resulting color is copied to clipboard in a format of your preference.</p>
    </div>
