</section>

<section class="b-features">
  <div class="b-features-wrap">
    <div class="b-features__item b-features_shortcuts">
      <h2>Under your fingertips</h2>
      <img src="/i/b-features_shortcuts.png" alt="Under your fingertips">
      <p>ColorSnapper is always here when you want it to be. No matter which application you are using, just press the chosen combination of the keys and it’s here!</p>
      <p>And for the precision sake, use arrows keys to position the cursor. Then use Space or Enter to pick a color.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="b-features__item b-features_format">
      <h2>In the format you want</h2>
      <img src="/i/b-features_format.png" alt="In the format you want">
      <p>Define up to 2 different formats and keep the ⌥ key pressed to pick a color in an alternative format.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="b-features__item">
      <h2>Pixel perfect...</h2>

      <div class="b-slide__item b-slide__item_2" style="display: none">
        <img src="/i/b-slide__item_2.png" alt="Pixel perfect">
      </div>

      <div class="b-slide__item b-slide__item_3" style="display: none">
        <img src="/i/b-slide__item_3.png" alt="Pixel perfect">
      </div>

      <div class="b-slide__item b-slide__item_4" style="display: none">
        <img src="/i/b-slide__item_4.png" alt="Pixel perfect">
      </div>

      <div class="b-slide__item b-slide__item_5" style="display: none">
        <img src="/i/b-slide__item_5.png" alt="Pixel perfect">
      </div>

      <div class="b-slide__item b-slide__item_6" style="display: none">
        <img src="/i/b-slide__item_6.png" alt="Pixel perfect">
      </div>

      <div class="b-slide__item b-slide__item_7" style="display: none">
        <img src="/i/b-slide__item_7.png" alt="Pixel perfect">
      </div>

      <div class="b-slide__item b-slide__item_8" style="display: none">
        <img src="/i/b-slide__item_8.png" alt="Pixel perfect">
      </div>

      <div class="b-slide__item b-slide__item_9" style="display: none">
        <img src="/i/b-slide__item_9.png" alt="Pixel perfect">
      </div>

      <div class="b-slide__slider">
        <div id="slider"></div>
      </div>
      <p>With ColorSnapper you can really see what&rsquo;s on your screen. With magnification from 2&times; till 11&times; you will see every aspect of your design.</p>
      <p>Really, just try it out by dragging the slider!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

